        ul
          li What is a graph database?
          li How can I query a graph?
          li What can I do with Neo4j?
        p &nbsp;
        button.btn.btn-cta(play-topic='concepts') Start Learning (5 minutes)
      .col-sm-4
        h3 
          img.img-responsive(src='images/code-snippet.png')
          | Jump into code
